      • exec

        public Project exec(TerminalScanner scan,
                    DataModel model,
                    User dummy3)
             throws CancelException,
                    java.lang.IllegalArgumentException
        Get a Project chosen by the person by presenting him a list of projects. The option list used will be determined by the list passed to GetProjectCmd(purecollections.PList) or setOptionsList(purecollections.PList). When this list is set to null the list of projects in the passed DataModel will be used.


        1. The system shows a list of existing projects.
        2. The person selects an existing project of the list.

        Specified by:
        exec in interface Cmd
        Parameters:
        scan - The scanner used to interact with the person.
        model - The model used for model access.
        dummy3 - Doesn't matter
        Returns:
        The chosen project.
        Throws:
        CancelException - When the users wants to abort the current cmd
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - If the given scan, model is null.
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - When the list of options is empty.
        See Also:
        GetObjectOfListCmd.exec(TerminalScanner, DataModel, User)
